' ============================================
' DEPENDENCIES - Priklausomybės
' ============================================

' Views → Controllers (front-end MVC)
"Šeimos nario posistemis"."Views" ..> "Šeimos nario posistemis"."Controllers" : uses

' Controllers → Services + Domain
"Šeimos nario posistemis"."Controllers" ..> "Services" : uses
"Šeimos nario posistemis"."Controllers" ..> "DomainModel" : uses entities
"Šeimos administravimo posistemis"."Controllers" ..> "Services" : uses
"Šeimos administravimo posistemis"."Controllers" ..> "DomainModel" : uses entities

' Services → Domain + DataAccess + External
"Services" ..> "DomainModel" : uses entities
"Services" ..> "DataAccess"."Repositories" : uses
"Services" ..> "ExternalServices" : calls

' DataAccess → Supabase + Core
"DataAccess"."Repositories" ..> "DataAccess"."SupabaseGateway" : uses
"DataAccess"."SupabaseGateway" ..> "Core"."Network"."SupabaseClient" : uses

' Subsystems → Core
"Šeimos nario posistemis" ..> "Core" : uses
"Šeimos administravimo posistemis" ..> "Core" : uses
"Services" ..> "Core" : uses

' Actors → UI / Controllers / Boundaries
"Actors"."Šeimos narys" ..> "Šeimos nario posistemis"."Views" : interacts
"Actors"."Šeimos administratorius" ..> "Šeimos administravimo posistemis"."Controllers" : interacts
"Actors"."GoogleAuthentication" ..> "Core"."Network"."HttpClient" : OAuth
"Actors"."GeminiAPI" ..> "ExternalServices"."GeminiServiceBoundary" : external API
"Actors"."MLKitOCR" ..> "ExternalServices"."OCRServiceBoundary" : external API
"Actors"."Parduotuvės svetainė" ..> "Services"."DealsScraperService" : provides data
"Actors"."SpoonacularAPI" ..> "ExternalServices"."SpoonacularServiceBoundary" : external API

' Navigation
"Šeimos nario posistemis"."Views"."NutritionPage" ..> "Šeimos nario posistemis"."Views"."MealPlanningPage" : navigates to

note right of "Šeimos nario posistemis"
  **Flutter App:**
  - Views = UI Boundaries (15 langų)
  - Controllers = BLoC objektai (Events → States)
  - Viskas vyksta klientėje (mobile/web app)
end note

note right of "DomainModel"
  **Bendras Domain Model:**
  - 19 Entities
  - 7 Enumerations
  - Naudojamas abiejose posistemėse
end note

note right of "Services"
  **Services = verslo logika:**
  - Koordinuoja Repositories + External Services
  - Naudoja Domain entities
  - Vyksta Flutter app viduje
end note

note bottom of "DataAccess"."SupabaseGateway"
  SupabaseGateway wrap'ina
  Core.Network.SupabaseClient
  (nėra dubliavimo)
end note

note top of "Saldytuvas Plus"
  **SVARBU: Loginė vs Fizinė Architektūra**
  
  **Ši diagrama rodo LOGINĘ architektūrą:**
  - Rodo KAS naudoja KĄ (priklausomybės)
  - DomainModel/DataAccess = bendri loginiai paketai
  - Entities/Repositories logiškai yra bendri (bet fiziniame kode yra feature-based)
  
  **Jūsų fizinė struktūra (lib/):**
  - lib/features/inventory/models/ - Entities (feature-based)
  - lib/features/inventory/repositories/ - Repositories (feature-based)
  - lib/services/ - Services (bendras)
  
  **Išvada:** Diagrama teisinga - rodo priklausomybes, ne failų vietas!
  
  **Flutter vs Django:**
  - Django: Frontend ↔ Backend (dvi sistemos)
  - Flutter: Viskas vienoje aplikacijoje (klientėje)
end note

@enduml
